        public StandardStationFactory​(java.lang.String state,

                              Point coordinates)
                       throws java.lang.Exception
        Creates a new standard station with a new ID, a given state, at a given time and a given point on the map
        Parameters:
        state - the state of the station : "ONSERVICE" for activate the station or "OFFLINE" for shut it down.
        time - the time of beginning of service of the station.
        coordinates - the coordinates of the station.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - thrown when the begin time or the state is misspelled.
